15. Yudkowsky, E. (2008). Artificial Intelligence as a Positive and Negative Factor in Global Risk. (AI risk analysis)

Acknowledgments

This work stands on the shoulders of countless researchers, philosophers, and engineers who have contributed to our understanding of intelligence, ethics, and wisdom. Special acknowledgment to the global community working toward beneficial AI and to the wisdom traditions that have guided humanity for millennia.

